{"data":[{"name":"92:1","price":"1. (அனைத்தையும்) மூடிக்கொள்ளும் (இருண்ட) இரவின் மீது சத்தியமாக! ","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6059,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā yaghshā ","translations":["By the night","when","it covers","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","yaghshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,1640],[3,1640,2775]]}},{"name":"92:2","price":"2. பிரகாசமுள்ள பகலின் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا تَجَلَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6060,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nahāri idhā tajallā ","translations":["And the day","when","it shines in brightness","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nahāri","idhā","tajallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2000],[2,2000,2570],[3,2570,3855]]}},{"name":"92:3","price":"3. ஆணையும் பெண்ணையும் படைத்தவன் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَمَا خَلَقَ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6061,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā khalaqa al-dhakara wal-unthā ","translations":["And He Who","created","the male","and the female","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","khalaqa","al-dhakara","wal-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1260],[3,1260,2170],[4,2170,4415]]}},{"name":"92:4","price":"4. (மனிதர்களே!) நிச்சயமாக உங்கள் முயற்சிகள் பலவாறாக இருக்கின்றன.","arabic":"إِنَّ سَعۡيَكُمۡ لَشَتَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6062,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna saʿyakum lashattā ","translations":["Indeed","your efforts","(are) surely diverse","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","saʿyakum","lashattā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,2330],[3,2330,3655]]}},{"name":"92:5","price":"5. ஆகவே, (உங்களில்) எவர் தானம் செய்து (அல்லாஹ்வுக்குப்) பயந்து,","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أَعۡطَىٰ وَٱتَّقَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6063,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ammā man aʿṭā wa-ittaqā ","translations":["Then as for","(him) who","gives","and fears","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ammā","man","aʿṭā","wa-ittaqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1740],[2,1740,2150],[3,2150,3050],[4,3050,4725]]}},{"name":"92:6","price":"6. (இந்த மார்க்கத்திலுள்ள) நல்ல காரியங்களையும் (நல்லதென்றே) உண்மையாக்கி வைக்கிறாரோ,","arabic":"وَصَدَّقَ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6064,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"waṣaddaqa bil-ḥus'nā ","translations":["And believes","in the best","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["waṣaddaqa","bil-ḥus'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,2425]]}},{"name":"92:7","price":"7. அவருக்கு சொர்க்கப் பாதையை நாம் எளிதாக்கித் தருவோம்.","arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6065,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fasanuyassiruhu lil'yus'rā ","translations":["Then We will ease him","towards [the] ease","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fasanuyassiruhu","lil'yus'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1790],[2,1790,3725]]}},{"name":"92:8","price":"8. எவன் கஞ்சத்தனம் செய்து (அல்லாஹ்வையும்) பொருட்படுத்தாது,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۢ بَخِلَ وَٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6066,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā man bakhila wa-is'taghnā ","translations":["But as for","(him) who","withholds","and considers himself free from need","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","man","bakhila","wa-is'taghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1720],[2,1720,2630],[3,2630,3250],[4,3250,4555]]}},{"name":"92:9","price":"9. (இம்மார்க்கத்திலுள்ள) நல்ல காரியங்களையும் பொய்யாக்கி வைக்கிறானோ,","arabic":"وَكَذَّبَ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6067,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wakadhaba bil-ḥus'nā ","translations":["And denies","the best","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wakadhaba","bil-ḥus'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2455]]}},{"name":"92:10","price":"10. அவனுக்குக் (கஷ்டத்திற்குரிய) நரகப் பாதையைத்தான் நாம் எளிதாக்கி வைப்போம்.","arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلۡعُسۡرَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6068,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fasanuyassiruhu lil'ʿus'rā ","translations":["Then We will ease him","towards [the] difficulty","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fasanuyassiruhu","lil'ʿus'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1760],[2,1760,3555]]}},{"name":"92:11","price":"11. அவன் (நரகத்தில்) விழுந்துவிட்டால், அவனுடைய பொருள் அவனுக்கு (ஒரு) பயனுமளிக்காது.","arabic":"وَمَا يُغۡنِي عَنۡهُ مَالُهُۥٓ إِذَا تَرَدَّىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6069,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yugh'nī ʿanhu māluhu idhā taraddā ","translations":["And not","will avail","him","his wealth","when","he falls","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yugh'nī","ʿanhu","māluhu","idhā","taraddā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1540],[3,1540,2130],[4,2130,4670],[5,4670,5280],[6,5280,6595]]}},{"name":"92:12","price":"12. நிச்சயமாக நேர்வழியை அறிவிப்பது நம்மீதுதான் கடமையாகும்.","arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا لَلۡهُدَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6070,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ʿalaynā lalhudā ","translations":["Indeed","upon Us","(is) the guidance","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ʿalaynā","lalhudā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,2250],[3,2250,3435]]}},{"name":"92:13","price":"13. நிச்சயமாக இம்மையும், மறுமையும் நமக்கே சொந்தமானவை!","arabic":"وَإِنَّ لَنَا لَلۡأٓخِرَةَ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6071,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-inna lanā lalākhirata wal-ūlā ","translations":["And indeed","for Us","(is) the Hereafter","and the first (life)","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-inna","lanā","lalākhirata","wal-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1360],[2,1360,2110],[3,2110,3550],[4,3550,5025]]}},{"name":"92:14","price":"14. (மக்காவாசிகளே!) கொழுந்து விட்டெரியும் நெருப்பைப் பற்றி நான் உங்களுக்கு அச்சமூட்டி எச்சரிக்கை செய்கிறேன்.","arabic":"فَأَنذَرۡتُكُمۡ نَارٗا تَلَظَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6072,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-andhartukum nāran talaẓẓā ","translations":["So I warn you","(of) a Fire","blazing","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-andhartukum","nāran","talaẓẓā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2650],[2,2650,4010],[3,4010,5555]]}},{"name":"92:15","price":"15. மிக்க துர்பாக்கியம் உடையவனைத் தவிர, (மற்றெவனும்) அதற்குள் செல்லமாட்டான்.","arabic":"لَا يَصۡلَىٰهَآ إِلَّا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6073,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yaṣlāhā illā al-ashqā ","translations":["Not","will burn (in) it","except","the most wretched","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yaṣlāhā","illā","al-ashqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,470],[2,470,3279],[3,3279,3899],[4,3899,5524]]}},{"name":"92:16","price":"16. அவன் (நம் வசனங்களைப்) பொய்யாக்கிப் புறக்கணித்துவிடுவான்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6074,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī kadhaba watawallā ","translations":["The one who","denied","and turned away","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","kadhaba","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,2000],[3,2000,3405]]}},{"name":"92:17","price":"17. இறையச்சமுடையவர்தான் அதிலிருந்து தப்பித்துக்கொள்வார்.","arabic":"وَسَيُجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَتۡقَى","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6075,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wasayujannabuhā al-atqā ","translations":["But will be removed from it","the righteous","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["wasayujannabuhā","al-atqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3040],[2,3040,4585]]}},{"name":"92:18","price":"18. அவர் (பாவத்திலிருந்து தன்னைப்) பரிசுத்தமாக்கிக் கொள்வதற்காக தன் பொருளை(த் தானமாக)க் கொடுப்பார்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يُؤۡتِي مَالَهُۥ يَتَزَكَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6076,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yu'tī mālahu yatazakkā ","translations":["The one who","gives","his wealth","(to) purify himself","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yu'tī","mālahu","yatazakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,1890],[3,1890,3000],[4,3000,4515]]}},{"name":"92:19","price":"19. தான் பதில் நன்மை செய்யக்கூடியவாறு எவருடைய நன்றியும் தன் மீது இருக்காது.","arabic":"وَمَا لِأَحَدٍ عِندَهُۥ مِن نِّعۡمَةٖ تُجۡزَىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6077,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā li-aḥadin ʿindahu min niʿ'matin tuj'zā ","translations":["And not","for anyone","with him","any","favor","to be recompensed","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","li-aḥadin","ʿindahu","min","niʿ'matin","tuj'zā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1650],[3,1650,3320],[4,3320,3620],[5,3620,6310],[6,6310,7405]]}},{"name":"92:20","price":"20. இருப்பினும், மிக்க மேலான தன் இறைவனின் திருமுகத்தை விரும்பியே தவிர (வேறு எதற்காகவும் தானம் செய்ய மாட்டார்).","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱبۡتِغَآءَ وَجۡهِ رَبِّهِ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6078,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"illā ib'tighāa wajhi rabbihi al-aʿlā ","translations":["Except","seeking","(the) Countenance","(of) his Lord","the Most High","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","ib'tighāa","wajhi","rabbihi","al-aʿlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,3409],[3,3409,3969],[4,3969,4879],[5,4879,6054]]}},{"name":"92:21","price":"21. (இறைவன் அவருக்கு அளிக்கும் கொடையைப் பற்றிப்) பின்னர் அவரும் திருப்தியடைவார்.","arabic":"وَلَسَوۡفَ يَرۡضَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6079,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"walasawfa yarḍā ","translations":["And soon, surely","he will be pleased","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["walasawfa","yarḍā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[2,1240,2285]]}}],"chapter":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail","Chapter Al-Lail","Lail","Surah Lail","Chapter Lail","Al Lail","Surah Al Lail","Chapter Al Lail","Surah 92","Chapter 92","The Night","الليل"],"version":{"key":"tamil_baqavi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ta","version":"1.0.1","last_update":1609966800,"title":"Tamil Translation - Abdulhamid Albaqoi","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Tamil by Sh. Abdulhamid Albaqoi"}}